data.description: Welcome home to this spacious condo, nestled in a gated community in the heart of the Medical Center. The open floor plan boasts recent updates, including appliances and flooring, seamlessly blending comfort, style, and convenience. Covered parking, storage, and both front and rear entrances enhance the practicality of this residence. Take advantage of community amenities, including a pool, dog park, and BBQ area. Don't let the opportunity slip by to make this space your own. The HOA Fee covers water service and common area maintenance, adding to the ease of living. With just minutes to IH 10 and 410, enjoy a swift commute to hospitals, shopping, and dining establishments. Your peaceful haven awaits!
